@eddie Great post! Its awesome that my approach has inspired you to choose more passive approach whenever possible. I'm still using Swarm for active "check-in" tracking, but even with such a great user experience, I still forget too often. Thankfully, I *also* passively track using Overland, so I can always go back later and fill in gaps if I want to.<br/>
<br/>
Now, we just need to convince Marco to add an RSS/Atom/JSON feed to overcast.fm :)
